These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-1::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, dannemann
1. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
2. the dannemann-smoker is not to the right of the dannemann-smoker##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2  |
| Cigar   | dannemann | aristoff |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-2::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: january, february
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far right##1
2. the person who's birthday is in january is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| Birthday   | february | january |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-3::.
City: hannover, boston
1. the person traveling to hannover is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to boston##5
2. the person traveling to boston is on the left or right of the person traveling to hannover##3
3. the person traveling to hannover is not to the right of the person traveling to hannover##8

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |    2     |
| City   | hannover | boston |

 #################################

 
